    "description": "<strong>Still be a Human</strong> 是一款动作类 Rogue，强调构建神器组合。 通过选择一个角色，你从阴影之塔的顶部下降，在你的路上你会遇到许多敌人，每个英雄的独特能力将有助于对抗他们，并将找到的神器放置在能力中 你不会给暗影教留下任何机会。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896810/extras/d8b1a094b9da13a37513a845ebd34f50.poster.avif?t=1668078988\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896810/extras/d8b1a094b9da13a37513a845ebd34f50.webm?t=1668078988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896810/extras/d8b1a094b9da13a37513a845ebd34f50.mp4?t=1668078988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >抢先体验版：</h2>[列表]<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 个角色 - 战士、墨水杀手和法师<br></li><li>30 件武器 - 每个英雄 10 件<br></li><li>25 件文物 - 每件都有自己独特的属性，从球状闪电到黑洞<br></li><li>6 块特色之石 - 随机获得的石头，可以提高你的角色属性<br></li><li>3 个地点 - 包括敌人、老板和陷阱<br></li><li>135 - 提升你的角色能力</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896810/extras/c48e123bbf51abc7694eeba605e5d6db.poster.avif?t=1668078988\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896810/extras/c48e123bbf51abc7694eeba605e5d6db.webm?t=1668078988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896810/extras/c48e123bbf51abc7694eeba605e5d6db.mp4?t=1668078988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
